'''第五十五届超级碗'''（{{lang-en|Super Bowl LV}}），是一场于2021年2月7日在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[坦帕|坦帕]][[雷蒙詹姆斯體育場|雷蒙詹姆斯體育場]]举行的[[美式橄榄球|美式橄榄球]]比赛，对阵双方为[[美国橄榄球联合会|美国橄榄球联合会]]当季冠军[[堪薩斯城酋長|堪薩斯城酋長]]和[[国家橄榄球联合会|国家橄榄球联合会]]当季冠军[[坦帕湾海盗|坦帕湾海盗]]，<ref name="LA-COVID-19">{{cite news|title=NFL is ready to call an audible or two if coronavirus forces schedule changes|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/story/2020-05-07/nfl-2020-schedule-release-goodell-changes-coronavirus|first=Sam|last=Fraser|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2020-05-07}}</ref>后者以31:9的比分获胜，球队领袖[[四分卫|四分卫]][[汤姆·布雷迪|汤姆·布雷迪]]获得[[超级碗最有价值球员|超级碗最有价值球员]]。<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.cnn.com/2021/02/07/us/chiefs-vs-buccaneers-super-bowl-lv/index.html | title = 
Tom Brady wins his 7th Super Bowl in his first year with the Buccaneers at age 43 | work = CNN | date = 2021-02-07 | accessdate = 2021-02-07}}</ref>这届超级碗是坦帕地区第五次举办超级碗，也是雷蒙詹姆斯體育場第三次举办超级碗。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sbnation.com/nfl/2018/2/4/16897244/2019-super-bowl-53-liii-location-date|title=2019 Super Bowl LIII Location and Date|access-date=2018-02-04}}</ref>受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，该届超级碗仅开放25,000名现场观众入场观看比赛，这也令该届超级碗成为史上现场观众人数最少的超级碗<ref name="official attendance expected">{{cite news|last=Patra|first=Kevin|title=Official attendance expected for Super Bowl LV: 25,000 fans, 30,000 cutouts|url=https://www.nfl.com/news/official-attendance-expected-for-super-bowl-lv-25-000-fans-30-000-cutouts|publisher=NFL Enterprises, LLC|website=NFL.com|date=2021-02-02|access-date=2021-02-03}}</ref>。

